==评价==
草莓棉花糖在英语地区得到了不少正面评价。[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]的Carlo Santos認為該作品以“以一種很直接的方式提供歡樂”並且提到“有種無聲無色地傳遞一種獨特的吸引力”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/strawberry-marshmallow/dvd-1|title=Strawberry Marshmallow Cute is as Cute does|accessdate=2007-01-18|last=Santos|first=Carlo|date=June 15, 2006|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|archive-date=2007-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070204075750/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/strawberry-marshmallow/dvd-1|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/strawberry-marshmallow/dvd-3|title=Strawberry Marshmallow Winter Adventures|accessdate=2007-01-18|last=Santos|first=Carlo|date=October 10, 2006|publisher=[[Anime_News_Network|Anime News Network]]|archive-date=2007-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070308111405/http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/review/strawberry-marshmallow/dvd-3|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{tsl|en|The_Comics_Journal|漫畫卷}}的Dirk Deppey認為作者能在幾乎沒有任何多余的承托就能爆发出其喜剧效果，并且运用非常纯熟的技巧和风度引出笑点。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tcj.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=471&Itemid=70|title=Strawberry Marshmallow|accessdate=2007-01-18|last=Deppey|first=Dirk|date=November 29, 2006|publisher=The Comic Journal|archive-date=2007-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930023729/http://www.tcj.com/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=471&Itemid=70|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{tsl|ja|Yuricon|百合控}}的Erica Friedman认为整个作品系列可爱得无法拒绝，<ref>{{Cite web|last=Friedman|first=Erica|url=http://okazu.yuricon.com/2005/05/11/yuri-manga-ichigo-mashimaro-volume-1/<!-- old-url=http://okazu.blogspot.com/2005/05/ichigo-mashimaro-volume-1.html -->|title=Yuri Manga: Ichigo Mashimaro, Volume 1|work=Okazu|publisher=Yuricon|date=May 10, 2005|accessdate=2007-04-03|archive-date=2015-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150922152529/http://okazu.yuricon.com/2005/05/11/yuri-manga-ichigo-mashimaro-volume-1/|dead-url=no}}</ref>不过同时批评英文代理没能将原作中出现的双关语和音效词做出注解。<ref>{{Cite web|last=Friedman|first=Erica|url=http://okazu.yuricon.com/2006/12/20/yuri-manga-strawberry-marshmallow-volume-2/<!-- old-[corrupted?]url=http://okazu.blogspot.com/2006/12/yuri-manga-strawberry-marshmallow_20.html -->|title=Okazu: Yuri Manga: Strawberry Marshmallow, Volume 2|work=Okazu|publisher=Yuricon|date=December 20, 2006|accessdate=2007-07-14|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303233442/http://okazu.yuricon.com/2006/12/20/yuri-manga-strawberry-marshmallow-volume-2/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[杰森·汤普森|杰森·汤普森]]在编写[[Manga:_The_Complete_Guide|漫画完全手册]]时，将本作和[[最后的制服|最后的制服]]并称，并且说本作是“纯真的少年眼中的女孩子世界”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.suvudu.com/2009/11/365-days-of-manga-day-66-the-last-uniform.html|title=365 Days of Manga, Day 66: The Last Uniform|publisher=Suvudu|last=Thompson|first=Jason|date=November 20, 2009|accessdate=November 20, 2009|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160624064955/http://suvudu.com/2009/11/365-days-of-manga-day-66-the-last-uniform.html|archive-date=2016-06-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

